  "title": "Contract Senior Finance Executive / Assistant Finance Manager (Education) - Up to 7.5K",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Process non-PO invoices, contracts for service, vendor creation, and staff claims</p></li><li><p>Ensure accurate and timely payments</p></li><li><p>Prepare finance schedules and management reports</p></li><li><p>Support month-end/year-end closing and account reconciliation</p></li><li><p>Liaise with stakeholders to resolve discrepancies</p></li><li><p>Assist with procurement activities (PR, PO, contract administration)</p></li><li><p>Support quotation/tender processes and evaluations</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with finance & procurement policies</p></li><li><p>Assist in audits and implement recommendations</p></li><li><p>Handle ad-hoc finance duties</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Min Degree in Accounting, Finance, Business, or equivalent</p></li><li><p><strong>Min. 7 years of relevant finance / payment / procurement experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of procurement processes and controls</p></li><li><p>Experience with financial systems (SAP Hana, Ariba preferred)</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented with strong deadline management</p></li><li><p>Good communication and stakeholder management skills</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Excel and MS Office<br /></p><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599).</p></li></ul>",
